    Package Info

    GPEDM-package GPEDM

    Gaussian Process regression for Empirical Dynamic Modeling

    Functions

    fitGP()

    Fit a GP model

    getR2()

    Calculate R-squared

    getconditionals()

    Get conditional responses from a GP model

    getrhomatrix()

    Get pairwise dynamic correlation matrix

    makelags()

    Generate delay vectors

    plot(<GPpred>)

    Plot predictions from a GP model

    posdef()

    Find nearest positive definite matrix

    predict(<GP>)

    Get predictions from a GP model

    summary(<GP>)

    Print a summary of a GP model

    NEFSC Fall Bottom Trawl Data (subset)
